(26877, 'Servipep 20mg 14 f.c. tab.', 'سيرفيبيب 20مجم 14 قرص', '', '10', 'Famotidine', 'Novartis', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Peptic ulcer.anti-histamine.h2 antagonist', '20mg', 'Famotidine is indicated in pediatric and adult patients (with the bodyweight of 40 kg and above) for the management of active duodenal ulcer (DU), active gastric ulcer, symptomatic non-erosive gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD), and erosive esophagitis due to GERD, diagnosed by biopsy.[L11139]
